node.title: Police release CCTV footage of woman missing 10 days
node.description: The police have released CCTV footage of the last known sighting of an Auckland woman who was reported missing 10 days ago.
node.content:
["The police have released CCTV footage of the last known sighting of an Auckland woman who was reported missing 10 days ago.", "", "
Cindy Li, 70. Photo: Supplied / NZ Police
", "", "
Footage of Li on the morning of her disappearance. Photo: Supplied / NZ Police
", "Despite extensive searches around the Sandringham area, the police have found no sign of 70-year-old Cindy Li.", "Given the length of time since she disappeared, the police said they have serious concerns for her safety.", "Li was last seen walking on Tranmere Road, wearing a pink jacket over a light-coloured top and white pants.", "The CCTV footage can be viewed in full on the Auckland City Police Facebook page."]
